/><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n[遍地開花] 貿發局100+員工：香港加油<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1365434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1365434</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6d6abed9e7e32a13f598b6664091877658ec70","tid":1364832,"uid":261166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:17:50.000Z","msg":"食環同路人 請開 TG group，<br />\n要團結全行，互通消息，自主抗爭！<br />\n<br />\n「遍地開花」合縱連橫，時機到了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1363346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1363346</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"115428c5b114b807606dafd1f58c34e4396ee42f","tid":1364832,"uid":38761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:45:53.000Z","msg":"各文職公務員，你仲唔出聲？<br />\n<br />\n我係一位對黑警暴行非常憤怒既媽咪。尤其是香港政府制度既不公，令佢地可以肆無忌彈踐踏我地既權利，市民面對佢地既暴行毫無招架之力<br />\n由我一位紀律部隊的親友口中得知，政府正為所有紀律部隊進行薪酬調整 Grade Structure Review GSR，上一次GSR已經是十年之前。而今次重點在於為警察大幅加薪，而且已經到達關鍵程序<br />\n我覺得我地一定要向GSR Committee 抗議，強烈反對為警察大加人工。個committee系成個review 入面係扮演「關鍵」角色，因為由佢地決定同向政府建議「加薪幅度有幾多」。 咁做係為左比黑警知道市民既憤怒，佢地既行為雖然得不到制裁，但市民仍有方法令佢地付出代價，而且阻止佢地加人工，亦遠比現存機制，能更有效令佢地受到驚嚇同懲罰<br />\n提交時間：2019/7/26 上午08:59<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilSecrets/posts/724166154679171?__xts__[0]=68.ARDkO4mmCYvfyFEvWCr2MLJSflhiZcRjDGRMsdj8QUxA-rlo7YDL1ThuIStxioFKifzO6ptpcfGlc7KQ-3vCUNa8o9Pbqb6jDKJCxZX82xEAntp5JT9j9zsIxGmv79zyA2jViazcYVmsK8OF47yYitBj1R7aq-WmlxtUrH8NOotY1int-bt-VDA8VIIUtumHIuaCKZrg8PZgFBO_RI02oo3Na-UnPAEKaCFMuYyJgIBeTobnp3kTp-kytBXBGxkUv8j2xJOhQO6cGtYkH3P7hkJjf605VZnLn7_TRUzT5boaVAZ8q9EzIIuMi9vnEfcgg-PqEjYQhazc4i4hUVfb9iq8IzscxDZzYoyFrP99QSpXRYnJ-VHPNgEV-MXoLVoT9y9EXhafVA0oCgBfNpclvxhZJ3pg8J0JxqinqMshbnR2_t0Wt21Y5FE6iAuNVysm5BbDj7FfqaZmCVM7ycl9aLo8cmELURAGnMbYwV8V7KayQ_TiYD8B2g